caveats:
  swe: '' # Caveats and disclaimers in Swedish
  eng: 'Sen*Lex lists the same item once for each proficiency level and type of use (productive vs receptive), if the item has been used at each of the levels, which means that, for example, the word "berg" (Eng. mountain) is provided five time, once for each level at which it occurs. This also means that the number of unique items is much less than the number of entries.' # Caveats and disclaimers in English

